Subject: Re: Deutsche Post Security Cup 2013

Hi,
 
we do accept individuals as a team of one - however, that single person
would have to "proove" in their application that they by themselve have
"enough" expertise in order to beat out other team applications (which would
definitively be possible). Teams are evaluated based on the skillset they
would bring to the contest and the teams that are perceived as the most
skillful are than allowed to the contest (we have to limit participation due
to organisational overhead).
 
Regards,
Jürgen Pabel
 
Jürgen Pabel
Information Security Officer E-POSTBRIEF

 

